sourcesContent: import { Component, Output } from '@angular/core'; @Component({ selector: 'app-manager-header', templateUrl: './manager-header.component.html', styleUrls: ['./manager-header.component.css'] }) export class ManagerHeaderComponent { @Output() toggleSidebarForMe: EventEmitter = new EventEmitter(); toggleSidebar() { this.toggleSidebarForMe.emit(); } }
